Most of the profit from Theatre (nearly 90%) comes from the raid's unique drops. The chance of a unique being received is 10.99% for a deathless raid regardless of group size, and is decreased for every death and per skipped room (which is 0 for nearly all raids). Upon receiving a unique drop, it is given to one of the players in the raid at random (with the MVP having a higher chance). The weighting for unique drops is:
